Equine encephalomyelitis (Eastern), Panama
----------------------------------------------
Information received on [and dated] 9 sep 2015 from Dr Bredio Velasco Denvers, Director Nacional, Direccion de Salud Animal, Ministerio de Desarrollo Agropecuario, Panama city, Panama

Summary:
Report type: immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 25 Jun 2015
Date of confirmation of the event: 3 Sep 2015
Reason for notification: reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 17 Sep 2014
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: Eastern equine encephalomyelitis virus
Nature of diagnosis: clinical, laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country

